    h2. *Overview*
    h3. *Business Justification*

    Images are needed to be pushed to the oke-native-steward tenancy to make a release of new Cloud Provider OCI images with Software upgrades. The {{ config2.property }} property which manage the cloud-provider-oci component for OKE clusters with kubernetes version {{config2.k8s_versions}} need to be updated with the latest software.

    h2. Executive Summary:

    *What is the purpose of this Change ticket?*

    {color:#00875a} To push latest Cloud provider oci images for Kubernetes {{config2.k8s_versions}} into oke-native-steward tenancy. The {{ config2.property }} property which manages the cloud-provider-oci component for OKE clusters with kubernetes versions {{config2.k8s_versions}} need to be updated with latest software. {color}

    *What does this Change request do (high level)?*

    {color:#00875a} The Change will execute shepherd flock releases to upload container images to OCIR in Steward Tenancy and updates the {{ config2.property }} for all OKE clusters {{config2.k8s_versions}} with the latest software. {color}

