    h3. Mapping update rollback validation
    ||Step||Process||
    |1.|For each type of release for each of the flocks, the flock release must reach "Succeeded" phase|
    |2.|Open Limits Admin UI to check the property or limit you intended to change is done. Limits Admin UI is accessible from the devops portal[https://devops.oci.oraclecorp.com/limits-admin-ui/property-definitions]. Please realm specific endpoint for accessing the portal|
    |3.|Select the correct realm, group name is "{_}clusters{_}". Enter the individual property names|
    |4.|Choose the "group" as "Clusters" and choose the desired region and click on search|
    |5.|Please find the following properties and verify values with version {{ config2.k8s_versions }} and mapping {{ config2.property }}|
